::Kaiser/The Dragoon::
       The Dragoon lands in the swamp a short distance from Tyrael and wisely 
stays silent.  He lowers his body down until it is flat on the ground with 
only his head up looking around for any signs of attack.  Kaiser, however, 
landed a great deal farther away from the others so as to be in a position to flank 
the enemy should the opportunity present itself.

--part1_c.11e92e10.2c06c6c9_boundary
